    "This lack of interpretability undermines the reliability of deep learning methods, thus limiting their use in clinical practice.",
    "To break through this constraint, visualization tools and techniques can be used to increase the transparency of the model and enhance interpretability.",
    "Several researchers have explored the application of weakly supervised semantic segmentation.",
